summary: Just a fun little mod that adds a miniature town with citizens and guards. Access it by going to Whiterun and looking for a trap door under the big purple tree.
descriptionHtml:
Just a fun little mod that adds a miniature town with citizens and guards. Access it by going to Whiterun and looking for a trap door under the big purple tree.

Once I add better packages to the citizens and guards and pretty the town up a bit, I\'ll give a much better description.

Plans: Quests to become Jarl of the Town.
author: Blitz54
